post.description:
Crea un ejercicio dentro de una lección. El campo "type" determina la estructura del campo JSONB "content".

📝 Tipos de ejercicios soportados y su estructura de contenido:

**quiz** — Preguntas de opción múltiple (multi-pregunta):
```json
{
"type": "quiz",
"content": {
"questions": [
{
"question": "What is public speaking?",
"options": ["Option A", "Option B", "Option C", "Option D"],
"correct_index": 0,
"explanation": "Option A is correct because..."
}
],
"points_per_question": 10
}
}
```

**reading** — Pasaje de lectura:
```json
{
"type": "reading",
"content": {
"title": "The Art of Speech",
"content": "Full reading text here...",
"reading_time_seconds": 120,
"points": 5
}
}
```

**oratory_minigame** — Desafío de oratoria con requisitos:
```json
{
"type": "oratory_minigame",
"content": {
"prompt": "Record a 30-second speech about...",
"topic": "Leadership",
"duration_seconds": 30,
"min_duration_seconds": 15,
"requirements": ["Clear introduction", "Use at least 3 key points", "Strong conclusion"],
"points": 20
}
}
```

**writing** — Ejercicio de escritura con requisitos:
```json
{
"type": "writing",
"content": {
"prompt": "Write a 200-word essay about leadership",
"min_words": 100,
"max_words": 500,
"requirements": ["Include a thesis", "Support with examples"],
"points": 20
}
}
```

**audio** — Ejercicio de grabación de audio:
```json
{
"type": "audio",
"content": {
"prompt": "Read this paragraph aloud...",
"duration_seconds": 60,
"points": 15
}
}
```

**video** — Ejercicio de grabación de video:
```json
{
"type": "video",
"content": {
"prompt": "Record a video introducing yourself...",
"duration_seconds": 120,
"points": 25
}
}
```

🔒 Requiere disqualquier token JWT (Authorization: Bearer <token>)
